task.summary: The template of Sorter is completed. Sorter is supported for any ComparingInterface implement for judging correlation between two BasePosition implements. The concrete ComparingInterface implement is given by BasePosition, which indicates correlation between two of this kind. WARNING, Work left to be finished: ! BasePosition.Swap safe implement ! BasePosition.ColorSorting_r2p safe implement

Introduce Layout, a sequential order of points in the Platform Beings should choose its position according to the Layout Sorter should sort according to the Layout and its order Platform should implement LayoutManip
Finish Stage Three: 1. Layout & Attachments 2. Sorter integrated into Grandpa and Serpent 3. Grandpa and Serpent control corresponding subordinates
